登友發現佢平安夜番左去高登呻吟<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum6.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6652154&amp;amp;type=HT&amp;amp;page=4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum6.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6652154%26amp%3Btype%3DHT%26amp%3Bpage%3D4&d=JoG46H50TOHn26Zb%2FLFuYGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=dc5ffedc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum6.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6652154&amp;amp;type=HT&amp;amp;page=4</a><br />\n<br />\n宜家又話自己冇退出高登潮流台玩具台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/84175/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/84175/page/1</a><br />\n退出都可以上去cap圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/84175/page/2/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/84175/page/2/</a>"},{"pid":"e5226e7c24e9c2225097d67f7ad0f09715dc0507","tid":88523,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T16:48:34.000Z","msg":"識食住條水未發到豬頭"},{"pid":"6731a74d2dfaa0e5badb9cb8a070575e7858f7fc","tid":88523,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T16:49:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正評<br />\n<br />\n睇到連支持達嘅人真係好撚噁心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n基本上達講咩都一定有人撐<br />\n<br />\n一反就屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個真"},{"pid":"a5af0db79a47a1d9646c2746ec9731a79aad6ee1","tid":88523,"uid":71959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T16:53:58.000Z","msg":"由達哥用老翻單野已經知班撚樣雙重標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cca13137b17d0c21c88fd525b37f77d5ff72b39","tid":88523,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T16:54:31.000Z","msg":"即係咁<br />\n有左連登 你睇ceo做野幾爽手？<br />\n又加快高登 同整apps<br />\n呢樣野代表咩？<br />\n代表你本身食開屎<br />\n而家有鮑魚食 食唔慣 想返去食屎<br />\n而家搭巴士地鐵 數據都西架啦<br />\n重要load個西網 load黎load去都唔得<br />\n返到屋企又係 放完工都無咩時間淨<br />\n連網頁版都一能樣慢 你叫人點能樣忍？<br />\n知唔知道點解你覺得高登無問題？ <br />\n唔係因為你食開屎咁簡單 <br />\n係因為你係個毒撚<br />\n日日坐係屋企到上高登，咁邊會慢呢<br />\n又大能把時間慢慢等佢load 反正都無人搵你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95d445dbcfa7e5c71ecf5a9722150e5acf2ee085","tid":88523,"uid":33498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T01:12:50.000Z","msg":"用翻版仲咁多籍口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a927b3570fadb91be1d6c996e1856f681782c1","tid":88523,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T02:21:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係咁<br />\n有左連登 你睇ceo做野幾爽手？<br />\n又加快高登 同整apps<br />\n呢樣野代表咩？<br />\n代表你本身食開屎<br />\n而家有鮑魚食 食唔慣 想返去食屎<br />\n而家搭巴士地鐵 數據都西架啦<br />\n重要load個西網 load黎load去都唔得<br />\n返到屋企又係 放完工都無咩時間淨<br />\n連網頁版都一能樣慢 你叫人點能樣忍？<br />\n知唔知道點解你覺得高登無問題？ <br />\n唔係因為你食開屎咁簡單 <br />\n係因為你係個毒撚<br />\n日日坐係屋企到上高登，咁邊會慢呢<br />\n又大能把時間慢慢等佢load 反正都無人搵你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁BACKUP撚整BACKUP真係方便左唔少人你又反<br />\n我9點半唔得閒睇可以第日係YOUTUBE再睇返<br />\n定係你係個毒撚<br />\n晚晚都可以捕住部電腦睇佢9點半呀"},{"pid":"6bfe5d826e711bd058048f6c60ba61487036355e","tid":88523,"uid":13257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T02:30:07.000Z","msg":"兩個比喻唔同啦<br />\n<br />\n我認同連登係抄，但佢係抄個論壇設計，d人係真係入黎連登留言。如果以前hkg+咁，直接拎高登server內容，個比喻就成立，但其實hkg+根本有拎授權而backup佬無，所以兩者更加唔同。<br />\n<br />\nbackup狗係成條片copy and paste擺上網，同連登唔同。要個比喻成立既話，係backup狗學達哥個style打機然後自己直播，咁就同連登一樣喇。"},{"pid":"dc044aa2a541d469200b48d3d34a1f41c9ef161f","tid":88523,"uid":72820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T02:36:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>即係咁<br />\n有左連登 你睇ceo做野幾爽手？<br />\n又加快高登 同整apps<br />\n呢樣野代表咩？<br />\n代表你本身食開屎<br />\n而家有鮑魚食 食唔慣 想返去食屎<br />\n而家搭巴士地鐵 數據都西架啦<br />\n重要load個西網 load黎load去都唔得<br />\n返到屋企又係 放完工都無咩時間淨<br />\n連網頁版都一能樣慢 你叫人點能樣忍？<br />\n知唔知道點解你覺得高登無問題？ <br />\n唔係因為你食開屎咁簡單 <br />\n係因為你係個毒撚<br />\n日日坐係屋企到上高登，咁邊會慢呢<br />\n又大能把時間慢慢等佢load 反正都無人搵你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁BACKUP撚整BACKUP真係方便左唔少人你又反<br />\n我9點半唔得閒睇可以第日係YOUTUBE再睇返<br />\n定係你係個毒撚<br />\n晚晚都可以捕住部電腦睇佢9點半呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果你覺得backup呢樣動作係好既，其實以我所知有channel係有達哥授權backup既 ，你大可以睇個個channel。無須睇backup佬，而家仲要撩交嗌咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋連登即使賺錢，佢都仲有server錢要每月俾，個度都唔少野，又要管理個forum，唔似backup佬咁上傳條片到youtube就輕輕鬆鬆有錢收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：平時唔睇達哥"},{"pid":"21b238393d473a6f86c5000cd90ac6aafe20bb9f","tid":88523,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T03:41:26.000Z","msg":"支持樓主"},{"pid":"cf82971fc4d732819a4fadf06775f98869a7b661","tid":88523,"uid":33495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T03:45:11.000Z","msg":"高登？backup狗？不了"},{"pid":"a2f9ffa981067a46ebae5064e461c00abbfe1ca3","tid":88523,"uid":4173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T03:51:34.000Z","msg":"你分清楚先比較啦傻仔，連登係一個更好嘅新平台，同高登係競爭關係(雖然高登無得爭)，backup佬係基於達哥嘅直播去生存，如果無左達哥，backup佬仲可以backup咩？backup樓豬比狗屌啲片？"},{"pid":"fb31f8111c29c0f9044703f1fecbaa2257d6c606","tid":88523,"uid":26106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T03:54:16.000Z","msg":"hkg+個程式係自己寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6060d0f853dedfb4ae10c96ea76e6598faa6fd4","tid":88523,"uid":40454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T04:02:35.000Z","msg":"Development maintenance server 唔洗錢唔洗時間阿 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  呢個價錢好合理喇"},{"pid":"7970138fe3e3a561cd15ed431b6bc7db3bf8b54a","tid":88523,"uid":38740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T04:34:12.000Z","msg":"系,樓主講既野好中肯"},{"pid":"b8413fe2da278577a3b040ca6b6d380560297719","tid":88523,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:18